rows.label: qst702803_msg0001
rows.name: That's weird... There's nothing in them.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0002
rows.name: Which means...

rows.label: qst702803_msg0003
rows.name: I should have guessed.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0004
rows.name:
Indeed, should have guessed.
But far too late for that now!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0005
rows.name:
It's the chairman of the
Chamber of Commerce!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0006
rows.name:
So hero-hero-friends were ones laying
waste to our precious goods...

rows.label: qst702803_msg0007
rows.name: It really is terrible shame.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0008
rows.name: Funny, I was thinking the same thing.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0009
rows.name:
If your goods are so precious to
you, why have you been leaving them
lying around all over the place?

rows.label: qst702803_msg0010
rows.name:
Pretty obvious he's up to some
shady business.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0011
rows.name:
Hold on. Let's give him the benefit
of the doubt.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0012
rows.name:
Tell us why you've been doing this,
Morumo.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0013
rows.name:
Meh... Morumo was not doing
anything wrong!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0014
rows.name:
Hazardous substances fetch high
prices on market. High prices lead
to good business.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0015
rows.name:
Any merchant worth their salt
live by such principle!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0016
rows.name:
So you'll resort to anything as long
as you can turn a profit?

rows.label: qst702803_msg0017
rows.name:
It so wrong to have dream worth
fighting for? This no time for taking
moral high ground!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0018
rows.name:
Says the Nopon spouting drivel
about dreams.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0019
rows.name:
Oh, please shut mouth. Morumo
was speaking in rhetoric!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0020
rows.name:
Morumo was quite fond of hero-hero-
friends. But now friends are enemies.
And enemies of Morumo must perish!
